<title>USA: Simulation Sciences licenses software.</title>
<headline>Simulation Sciences licenses software.</headline>
<dateline>BREA, Calif. 1997-04-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Simulation Sciences Inc on Monday said it has signed a $525,000 licensing deal with Amoco Corp under which its Worldwide Engineering and Construction division will use Simulation Sciences' Visual Flare software.</p>
<p>The agreement covers maintenance and license fees for Visual Flare, which will be used by Amoco engineers worldwide.</p>
<p>Visual Flare provides process engineers with a tool for designing and rating flare relief systems in a standard Microsoft Windows environment.</p>
